%% Server-mode search + pagination (useListController)
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    actor User as Admin User
    participant Toolbar as AdminTableToolbar
    participant Ctl as useListController
    participant Guard as AbortController /<br/>request-id guard
    participant Api as ProductsApi.getProducts
    participant BE as Backend GET /products
    participant DT as DataTable

    Note over User,DT: SEARCH PATH (debounced)
    User->>Toolbar: keystroke
    Toolbar->>Ctl: setSearch(term)
    activate Ctl
    Ctl->>Ctl: search.value = term (sync)<br/>page = 1 (reset)
    Ctl-->>DT: status = "loading" (optimistic)
    deactivate Ctl
    Note right of Ctl: debounce 300ms

    Ctl->>Guard: run() — abort prior request,<br/>reqId = ++counter (monotonic)
    activate Guard
    Guard->>Api: fetcher(query, signal)
    Note over Api,BE: free-text `search` is NOT sent —<br/>GET /products has no search param today<br/>(ESCALATION: not yet supported)
    Api->>BE: GET /products?page=1&page_size=n&…
    BE-->>Api: 200 { products, pagination }
    Api-->>Guard: response
    deactivate Guard

    alt reqId is current (not superseded)
        Guard->>Ctl: apply result
        Ctl->>Ctl: items = data<br/>pagination = meta<br/>status = "success"
        Ctl-->>DT: re-render rows + pagination
    else reqId superseded by a newer run()
        Guard-->>Guard: drop stale/late response<br/>(no state mutation)
        Note right of Guard: prevents out-of-order overwrite
    end

    Note over User,DT: PAGINATION PATH (immediate, no debounce)
    User->>Toolbar: click page n
    Toolbar->>Ctl: setPage(n)
    Ctl->>Guard: run() immediately (no debounce)
    Guard->>Api: fetcher(query, signal)
    Api->>BE: GET /products?page=n&page_size=…
    BE-->>Api: 200 { products, pagination }
    Api-->>Guard: response
    Guard->>Ctl: apply (if current reqId)
    Ctl-->>DT: re-render
